- Reach: 3,000 users/quarter
- Impact: MEDIUM (1.0) - Nice-to-have
- Confidence: 100% - Simple implementation
- Effort: 2 person-weeks
- RICE Score: 150 → Priority 3

Feature C: Real-time Collaboration
- Reach: 10,000 users/quarter
- Impact: VERY HIGH (5.0) - Game-changer
